<item>
            <title>[OAK-1719] Missing commit hooks in upgrade</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-1719</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There&apos;s a TODO in the RepositoryUpgrade class about missing commit hooks. For example the PermissionHook isn&apos;t currently run as a part of the upgrade, which breaks permission evaluation even though the actual ACL nodes are present after the upgrade.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12707704">OAK-1719</key>
            <summary>Missing commit hooks in upgrade</summary>
